      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c922",
      "text": "京大サマーデザインスクール2014京大サマーデザインスクール2014西尾泰和(c)2014西尾泰和(サイボウズ・ラボ)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c923",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c924",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-02.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c925",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングブレインストーミングブレインストーミング",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c926",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c927",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-03.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c928",
      "text": "Q:ブレインストーミングってアイデア出しの方法でしょ?[学び方]とどう関係があるの?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405678
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c929",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c92a",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-04.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c92b",
      "text": "アイデアと仮説と計画と“わかった\"気持ちは根が共通",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405686
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c92c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c92d",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-05.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c92e",
      "text": "アイデアは実行して検証しなければうまくいくかわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405812
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c92f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c930",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-06.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c931",
      "text": "仮説は実験して検証しなければ正しい仮説かわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405867
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c932",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c933",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-07.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c934",
      "text": "計画は実行して検証しなければ期待通りになるかわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405862
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c935",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c936",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-08.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c937",
      "text": "“わかった\"という気持ちは実行して検証しなければ本当にわかっているか不明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405878
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c938",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c939",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-09.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c93a",
      "text": "この4つはすべて“[知識の結合]によって新しく生み出され今後検証が必要なもの\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405901
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c93b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c93c",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-10.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c93d",
      "text": "[KJ法]も発想支援の方法であると同時に“わかる\"ための手法である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405918
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c93e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c93f",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-11.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c940",
      "text": "このスライドの目的",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405943
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28e1f6aff09e00000083d4",
      "text": "ブレストに関する思い込みを取り除く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529405943,
      "updated": 1529405943
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c941",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c942",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-12.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c943",
      "text": "“ブレインストーミング\"オズボーンによる造語",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405954
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28e202aff09e00000083d5",
      "text": " 1950年頃",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529405954,
      "updated": 1529405955
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c944",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c945",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-13.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c946",
      "text": "よく“ブレストのルール\"として紹介される4項目",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405962
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c947",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c948",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-14.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c949",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングの4原則",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529406039
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dd68aff09e00000083c3",
      "text": " 判断しない・結論を出さない([結論厳禁])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404777,
      "updated": 1529406006
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dd6eaff09e00000083c4",
      "text": "  自由なアイデア抽出を制限するような、判断・結論は慎む。…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404783,
      "updated": 1529404787
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dd73aff09e00000083c5",
      "text": " 粗野な考えを歓迎する([自由奔放])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404787,
      "updated": 1529404831
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dd76aff09e00000083c6",
      "text": "  誰もが思いつきそうなアイデアよりも、奇抜な考え方やユニークで斬新なアイデアを重視する。…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404790,
      "updated": 1529404795
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dd7aaff09e00000083c7",
      "text": " 量を重視する([質より量])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404795,
      "updated": 1529404844
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dd7eaff09e00000083c8",
      "text": "  様々な角度から、多くのアイデアを出す。…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404798,
      "updated": 1529404801
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dd81aff09e00000083c9",
      "text": " アイディアを結合し発展させる([結合改善])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404801,
      "updated": 1529404847
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dd85aff09e00000083ca",
      "text": "  別々のアイデアをくっつけたり一部を変化させたりすることで、新たな[アイデア]を生み出していく。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404806,
      "updated": 1529406015
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28e23eaff09e00000083d6",
      "text": "  他人の意見に便乗することが推奨される。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529406015,
      "updated": 1529406015
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dd89aff09e00000083cb",
      "text": " Wikipedia「ブレインストーミング」より抜粋",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404809,
      "updated": 1529404810
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c94a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c94b",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-15.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c94c",
      "text": "このルールの出典は?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529406032
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c94d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c94e",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-16.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c94f",
      "text": "“開会に際してリーダーは[問題の提示]とともに次の事柄を説明すべきである。(1)…(2)…(3)…(4)…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529406124
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28e2acaff09e00000083d7",
      "text": "オズボーン『[創造力を生かす]』p.272太字は筆者による",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529406124,
      "updated": 1529406124
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c950",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c951",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-17.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c952",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングリーダーはこれらの注意事項を自分の言葉で述べるべきである。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529406141
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28e2bcaff09e00000083d8",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングは常に非公式のものであるべきだからである。\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529406141,
      "updated": 1529406148
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28e2c3aff09e00000083d9",
      "text": "『創造力を生かす』p.273太字は筆者による",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529406148,
      "updated": 1529406148
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c953",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c954",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-18.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c955",
      "text": "・最初に問題を提示する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529406172
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28e2dcaff09e00000083da",
      "text": "・4つの注意事項を自分の言葉で述べる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529406172,
      "updated": 1529406172
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c956",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c957",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-19.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c958",
      "text": "これで全部? NO!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529406183
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c959",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c95a",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-20.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c95b",
      "text": "“厳密に正式に行わねばならない唯一の事柄は、提出された[すべてのアイデアの記録]である。\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529406209
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28e2f2aff09e00000083db",
      "text": "『創造力を生かす』p.273太字は筆者による",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529406195,
      "updated": 1529406195
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c95c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c95d",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-21.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c95e",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529404946
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28de11aff09e00000083cc",
      "text": "・すべてのアイデアを記録",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404946,
      "updated": 1529404948
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28de13aff09e00000083cd",
      "text": "・最初に問題を提示する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404948,
      "updated": 1529404950
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28de15aff09e00000083ce",
      "text": "・4つの注意事項を自分の言葉で述べる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404950,
      "updated": 1529404953
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28de19aff09e00000083cf",
      "text": "すべてのアイデアを記録することが一番重要なルール",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404953,
      "updated": 1529404953
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c95f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c960",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-22.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c961",
      "text": "“アイデアの流れを何かに書き留めてメンバ全員に見えるようにしよう\" IDEOが導入している追加ルール。『[発想する会社]!』p.70",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529406265
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c962",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c963",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-23.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28de33aff09e00000083d0",
      "text": "1986年に書かれた本でも“記録係が片端からメモする\"と書かれている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404980,
      "updated": 1529404983
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28de37aff09e00000083d1",
      "text": "なぜ記録の重要性が忘れ去られてしまったのか…『[思考の整理学]』p.168",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529404983,
      "updated": 1529404983
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c965",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c966",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-24.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c967",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングオズボーンはこうも言う: “この記録の写しが会議後全員に渡るようにすること\"『創造力を生かす』p.273太字は筆者による",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c968",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c969",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-25.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c96a",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングここまでのまとめ“アイデアを記録する\"がもっとも重要なルールこれをないがしろにしているケースがすごく多い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c96b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c96c",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-26.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c96d",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングブレストって口頭でアイデアを言い合う硬くない会議のことでしょ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c96e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c96f",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-27.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c970",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングブレストって口頭でアイデアを言い合う硬くない会議のことでしょ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c971",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c972",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-28.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c973",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングオズボーンの提唱後50件以上もの実験によって意外な事実が明らかに…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c974",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c975",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-29.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c976",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405350
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dfa4aff09e00000083d2",
      "text": "口頭で行う場合複数人のグループでやるより個別にやったほうがアイデアの量も質も高い McGrath(1984)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529405350,
      "updated": 1529405353
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c977",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c978",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-30.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c979",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング1.生産性の阻害他人の話を聞くことが自分の考える時間を奪う話題が固定化する、など『[凡才の集団は孤高の天才に勝る]』p.84",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392559
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c97a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c97b",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-31.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c97c",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング2.社会的抑制他のメンバにどう思われるか心配して発言できない『凡才の集団は孤高の天才に勝る』p.84",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c97d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c97e",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-32.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c97f",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング3.社会的怠惰責任がグループに分散し、個々人の必死さが失われる『凡才の集団は孤高の天才に勝る』p.84",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c980",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c981",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-33.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c982",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングこの問題を解決する方法は?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c983",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c984",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-34.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c985",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング“ブレインライティング\"個々人で書いてから共有する高橋誠“[ブレインライティング]短時間で大量のアイデアを叩き出す「沈黙の発想会議」\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392571
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c986",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c987",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-35.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c988",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング“電子ブレインストーミング\"口頭での発言をチャットで置き換えるこの方法は必要なら匿名化も可能という特長がある。Dennis and Valacich(1993) [Computer brainstorms]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392582
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c989",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c98a",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-36.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c98b",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング“グループウェアはコンピュータでブレインストーミングの舞台を作ろうというもの\"『[組織とグループウェア]』",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392610
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c98c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c98d",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-37.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c98e",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングここまでのまとめ“口頭\"は必須ではないむしろ生産性を損ねる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c98f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c990",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-38.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c991",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング個人でもブレストの訓練後アイデアの量が増す→ひとりでやっても有益『凡才の集団は孤高の天才に勝る』",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c992",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c993",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-39.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c994",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング書いてから共有する→同じ時間にやる必要がない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c995",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c996",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-40.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c997",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング“インターネットの普及により大規模なアイデアの収集が容易になった\"『[クラウドストーミング]』",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392631
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c998",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c999",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-41.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c99a",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング“チームメンバが集まる\"というイメージがそぐわない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c99b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c99c",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-42.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c99d",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングブレストの原理を応用して見かけの異なった手法がつくりだされてきている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c99e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c99f",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-43.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a0",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング“ブレストとはだ\"と決めつけるのではなくwhyを考えることが大事",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a2",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-44.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a3",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングブレストの問題点「質より量」しかし量が多すぎると人間が圧倒されてしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a5",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-45.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a6",
      "text": "ブレインストーミング一つの解決策は投票IDEOではブレスト終了後出席メンバーが気に入ったアイデアに投票する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a8",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-46.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9a9",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングもう一つの解決策はKJ法視野を広く使うことで一度に作業記憶に載る情報の量を増やす",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9ab",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-47.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9ac",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングこのワークの基本構造もブレスト→KJ法「各自が書いてから共有」は「アイデアの記録と配布」に相当",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9ae",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-48.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9af",
      "text": "参考文献",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529405381
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28dfc5aff09e00000083d3",
      "text": "•A.オスボーン(2008) “創造力を生かす:アイディアを得る38の方法\"豊田晃訳,創元社トム・ケリー,ジョナサン・リットマン(2002) “発想する会社! 世界最高のデザイン・ファームIDEOに学ぶイノベーションの技法\",鈴木主税訳,秀岡尚子訳,早川書房外山滋比古(1986) \"思考の整理学\"ちくま文庫高橋誠(2007)\"ブレインライティング-短時間で大量のアイデアを叩き出す「沈黙の発想会議」\" McGrath, J. E. (1984) \"[Groups: Interaction and performance]\" Englewood Cliffs, NJ: Prentice Hall Alan R. Dennis and Joseph S. Valacich (1993) \"Computer Brainstorms: More Heads Are Better Than One\" Journal of Applied Psychology 1993, Vol 78, No. 4, 531-537キース・ソーヤー(2009) \"[凡才の集団は孤高の天才に勝る]ー「グループ・ジーニアス」が生み出すものすごいアイデア\"ダイヤモンド社ショーン・エイブラハムソン(2014) \"クラウドストーミング-組織外の力をフルに活用したアイディアのつくり方\"阪急コミュニケーションズ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529405381,
      "updated": 1529405429
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9b1",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-49.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9b2",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングオズボーンが言っていること“提案の恩恵を受ける人たちからの簡単な感謝状を全員に配布する\"『創造力を生かす』p.273",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9b3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9b4",
      "text": "[http://nhiro.org/kuds2014/brainstorming/page-50.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
    {
      "id": "5b28acfdaff09e0000a7c9b5",
      "text": "ブレインストーミングオズボーンが言っていること“アイデアが採用される場合には、会議の人たちにその旨を報告して彼らを激励する\"『創造力を生かす』p.273",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1529392382,
      "updated": 1529392382
    },
